description:
She’s back for a much-requested part 2!

Highest Self Podcast listeners LOVED Danielle and had a LOT more questions for her, so I brought her back for a Q+A episode to answer YOUR pressing astrology questions!

In this episode, we discuss:
-What your sun, moon and rising mean
-What is means if they’re in the same planet
-Why the moon cycle at your time of birth matters
-How Danielle predicted my engagement through my chart
-What eclipse season really means
